Claude Mérelle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claude_M%C3%A9relle 0 Claude Mérelle (17 May 1888 – 16 December 1976) was a French stage and film actress who appeared in numerous films during the silent film era of the early 1910s through the late 1920s.
